
// This Hyperlambda code replaces occurrences of a placeholder string [[ainiro_watermark]] within the node referenced by [.result] with a watermark string. The watermark string is retrieved using [config.get] from the configuration key "magic:watermark". If the configuration key does not exist, it defaults to "Powered by <a href=\"https://ainiro.io\" target=\"_blank\">AINIRO.IO</a>". The [get-first-value] slot ensures that the first available value is used for the replacement.
strings.replace:x:@.result
   .:[[ainiro_watermark]]
   get-first-value
      config.get:"magic:watermark"
      .:"Powered by <a href=\"https://ainiro.io\" target=\"_blank\">AINIRO.IO</a>"
